paths.summary: Get the selected tile group details

name: CoreAPI Run_TileGroup
description: API to access results of Planet 9 Run_TileGroup Details.
about:
Description

Planet 9-Run_TileGroup maintains the groups of the Planet 9 tiles.

API Run_TileGroup is the API to access the tile group and to perform the REST operations.

You can use this API in your app when you want to get a tile group list, a single group details, Delete the group, or create the new group. The tile group can be added to a tile group to maintain the hierarchy level.

Every app must have the right roles (permissions) that enable access to the tile groups in your system.
